criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient aged 6 to 16 years;

          -  Patient diagnosed for a malignant pathology for at least one month and maximum 2
             months;

          -  Patient treated at the IHOPe;

          -  Non-opposition of the parents and the child under study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Difficulty speaking and understanding French;

          -  Patient who is not able to express himself because the somatic medical conditions do
             not allow a verbal exchange.
